* Code is 15% load on server and 85% on client with the help of special Jquery addon created by me :p

Example :

        new JQD.winSys({
                    WindowTitle: 'Gen win #1',
                    IconId : {{=i.id}},
                    IconX : {{=i.x}},
                    IconY : {{=i.y}},
                    TemplateUrl : 'asd'
      }).buildWindow();

=== Will directly create a new window set on client side web browser !

